item.title: CVE-2022-4656|2024-08-03T01:48:38.893Z -- unknown -- wp%20visitor%20statistics%20%28real%20time%20traffic%29
item.description: The WP Visitor Statistics (Real Time Traffic) WordPress plugin before 6.5 does not validate and escape one of its shortcode attributes, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attack.
